window.bookSummaryJSON = "The Pinhoes don't want the Chrestomanci to find out that they've been misusing their magic, but when Cat finds a mysterious old egg at Gammer's place, the Chrestomanci is sure to notice. <p> Author Diana Wynne Jones has won the prestigious Guardian and Mythopoeic Awards. <i>The Pinhoe Egg</i>, the fifth book in her popular Chrestomanci series, brings back Cat Chant.</p>"; 
